item.title: [HIVE-19619] Allow comparisons between doubles and bigints
item.description: Hive doesn't allow binary comparison between doubles and bigints. That is overly restrictive since all other DBs (mysql, postgres, oracle and sql server) allows that.
item.summary: Allow comparisons between doubles and bigints

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.
